title: Jenkins and Jonez - Matt Sullivan Details His Steph Curry Profile

description:
The guys discuss Robert Sarver’s suspension, a Raggedy Old Rock, and Tom Brady vs. Gisele before being joined by Matt Sullivan to detail his Steph Curry profile. Then they talk about cheating in chess and give their House of Dragon recap. #Volume #Herd
